      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNNY STRIDE (1) missed the frame latest (22.77) when eighth over 390m at this track in a Grade 5. Has already won two times from this draw. Looks the one to beat with even luck. IVORY HAMADA (6) doesn't show much early dash but winds into his races, two back missing the frame but last time hitting the line hard to place when third (28.33) in a Grade 4/5 at Bendigo last time. Solid record here winning three races. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Hard to beat again. MARSHALL BEAR (2) was well backed last start but ran below expectations when seventh (22.98), beaten 14 lengths. Has ability and can atone. PAW VADA (3) generally performs well from this box.",
